column117:
I did not know anything about the ship or the mission and I did not see any positive outcome for me to ask for these kind of information. I do not know much about space and stuff....
Therefore I only based my decisions on two aspects.
First: Take the route that deals with problems first/or let you take the other route if the direct confrontation does not work. For example: Use the satellites and the Lasers, because they deal with problems from a larger distance at let you (maybe) react later if needed.
Second: As I don't know anything about space/ships/missions/lasers.... try to find out if one of the robots has constantly better ideas. Therefore giving one of the robots at a time more energy and see what happens. If it succeeds, stay with it. If it fails give him/it another try. If it fails again, try the other one.
Sadly with this approach their suggestions an characters hat not much to do with how I decided.
